### SG-036 P1 — Top-10 CRUD coverage 보강 (Cycle 9, 2026-05-12)
###
### 배경:
###   integration-tests vs BO routers 정합성 분석 (Cycle 9):
###   .http 59 unique vs router 137 unique → coverage 19.7% (27/137).
###   110 uncovered + 26 orphan = 136 mismatch (1차 92 추정 → 정밀 136).
###
### Scope:
###   P1-core-list 9 + P1-core-create 7 + P1-core-update 25 중에서 사용자/운영
###   영향 최상위 10건만 본 cycle. 잔여는 Cycle 10~ 분할 PR.
###
### Schema 정합 (BO src/models/schemas.py 기준):
###   SeriesCreate: competition_id, series_name, year, begin_at, end_at, time_zone, currency
###   EventCreate: series_id, event_no, event_name, game_type, bet_structure, table_size
###   CompetitionCreate: name, competition_type, competition_tag
###   PlayerCreate: first_name, last_name, wsop_id?, nationality?, country_code?
###   UserCreate: email, password, display_name, role
###   BlindStructureCreate: name, levels[]
###
### Cycle 9 priority matrix (108 P1 uncovered → top 10):
###   1. GET  /api/v1/series              (사용자 ↑↑ — Lobby 최상위 list)
###   2. GET  /api/v1/competitions        (운영 ↑ — Series 부모)
###   3. GET  /api/v1/tables              (사용자 ↑↑ — Lobby/CC 진입)
###   4. GET  /api/v1/players             (운영 ↑ — Player 관리)
###   5. GET  /api/v1/users               (RBAC critical — admin 화면)
###   6. GET  /api/v1/blind-structures    (운영 ↑ — Final Table)
###   7. POST /api/v1/series              (운영 ↑↑ — series 신규)
###   8. POST /api/v1/competitions        (운영 ↑ — 최상위 entity)
###   9. POST /api/v1/players             (운영 ↑ — player 등록)
###  10. POST /api/v1/users               (RBAC critical — admin 만)
###
### 잔여 (Cycle 10+ 분할):
###   - P1-core-update/delete 25건 (PUT/PATCH/DELETE)
###   - P1-core-read 10건 (GET .../{id})
###   - P2 auth-2fa/audit/settings 16건
###   - P3 reports/sync 13건
###   - P4 clock/seats/skin-action 등 30건
###
### Source: SG-036 Spec_Gap_Registry §4.5 + integration-tests/_audit/sg036-cycle9/

@host = http://localhost:18001
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}
@viewer_token = {{$dotenv VIEWER_JWT}}

### 70.1 GET /api/v1/series — list series (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/series?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답:
# 200 OK
# {
#   "data": [SeriesResponse, ...],
#   "meta": { "skip": 0, "limit": 20, "total": <int> }
# }
# RBAC: get_current_user (viewer 이상). 401 = AUTH_TOKEN_MISSING/INVALID.

### 70.2 GET /api/v1/competitions — list competitions (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/competitions?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[CompetitionResponse[]] + meta total.
# RBAC: get_current_user.

### 70.3 GET /api/v1/tables — list tables (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tables
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[TableResponse[]].
# Lobby 진입 시 최초 호출. RBAC: get_current_user.

### 70.4 GET /api/v1/players — list players (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/players?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[PlayerResponse[]] + pagination meta.
# 운영 도구: Player 검색/등록 화면 진입.

### 70.5 GET /api/v1/users — list users (admin only)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users?skip=0&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[UserResponse[]].
# RBAC critical: require_role("admin"). 403 = AUTH_INSUFFICIENT_ROLE (viewer/operator).
# 검증 핵심: 403 분기 — viewer_token 으로 호출 시 거부.

### 70.5b GET /api/v1/users — viewer 거부 (403)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: 403 Forbidden, AUTH_INSUFFICIENT_ROLE.
# RBAC 분기 검증 (admin only endpoint).

### 70.6 GET /api/v1/blind-structures — list (viewer OK)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

# 예상 응답: ApiResponse[BlindStructureResponse[]] (각 항목에 levels 포함).
# Final Table 시 blind level 선택 진입.

### 70.7 POST /api/v1/series — create series (admin only)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/series
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "competition_id": 1,
  "series_name": "WSOP 2026 Main Event",
  "year": 2026,
  "begin_at": "2026-07-01T00:00:00Z",
  "end_at": "2026-07-15T23:59:59Z",
  "time_zone": "America/Los_Angeles",
  "currency": "USD",
  "country_code": "US"
}

# 예상 응답: 201 Created + ApiResponse[SeriesResponse].
# RBAC: require_role("admin"). 사전 조건: competition_id=1 존재 (FK 검증).

### 70.8 POST /api/v1/competitions — create competition (admin only)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/competitions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "WSOP",
  "competition_type": 0,
  "competition_tag": 0
}

# 예상 응답: 201 Created + ApiResponse[CompetitionResponse].
# 최상위 entity (Series 부모). 단순 schema 검증용.

### 70.9 POST /api/v1/players — create player (admin only)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/players
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Daniel",
  "last_name": "Negreanu",
  "wsop_id": "WSOP-12345",
  "nationality": "Canada",
  "country_code": "CA"
}

# 예상 응답: 201 Created + ApiResponse[PlayerResponse].
# RBAC: require_role("admin"). wsop_id unique 검증.

### 70.10 POST /api/v1/users — create user (admin only)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "operator1@cycle9.test",
  "password": "Operator!Test123",
  "display_name": "Cycle 9 Operator",
  "role": "operator"
}

# 예상 응답: 201 Created + ApiResponse[UserResponse].
# RBAC critical: require_role("admin"). 403 = AUTH_INSUFFICIENT_ROLE.
# email unique 검증 — 중복 시 409 또는 400.

### 70.10b POST /api/v1/users — viewer 거부 (403)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "denied@cycle9.test",
  "password": "Denied!Test123",
  "display_name": "Should Fail",
  "role": "viewer"
}

# 예상 응답: 403 Forbidden, AUTH_INSUFFICIENT_ROLE.
# admin only endpoint 거부 분기 검증.
